The documentation [home page](/doxee-platform/docs/getting-started#home-page) is the central hub for anyone looking for Doxee product documentation. Let us show you the most important parts:

![](data:image/png;base64,)

- ![Doxee University.png](data:image/png;base64,)**logo - **Jump back to the home page at any time

- **Top menu bar - **Quick navigation to all documentation articles, the glossary of terms, [training](https://university.doxee.com/), and the [Doxee company home page](https://www.doxee.com/)

- ![](data:image/png;base64,)**Portal news button - **See newly updated articles

- ![](data:image/png;base64,) **Language selector - **Switch documentation language to English or German.

- **User profile icon - **See your user profile information briefly

- ![](data:image/png;base64,)** Brose all articles button - **Browse the entire documentation portal with a hierarchical tree navigator

- ![](data:image/png;base64,) **Whats new button - **Overview of the most recently updated articles

- ![](data:image/png;base64,) **AI-powered search bar -** Free-text deep search with AI Assistance

- ![](data:image/png;base64,)**Getting started box -** General information about getting started with the documentation portal

- ![](data:image/png;base64,) **Product updates box -** Overview of the product updates, including release notes
